    "en": {
      "title": "Iran's support to trade and investment sectors",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Hashem Ashjazadeh, the Iranian ambassador, says that he will support the development of bilateral relations in the fields of trade and investment.",
        "He said this in a discussion held this afternoon with President Gotabaya Rajapaksa at the President's House in Fort Colombo.",
        "The possibility of implementing an oil exchange program along with Sri Lanka's tea exports was also discussed at length."
      ],
